notes:
BPHS Birth Time Rectification Methodology:
Source: Brihat Parashar Hora Shastra - Chapter 4 (लग्नाध्याय)

Key Verses Implemented:
- Gulika Calculation: BPHS 4.1-4.3 (गुलिक गणना)
- Pranapada (Madhya): BPHS 4.5 (घटी चतुर्गुणा...)
- Pranapada (Sphuta): BPHS 4.7 (स्वेष्टकालं पलीकृत्य...)
- Degree Matching: BPHS 4.6 (लग्नांशप्राणांशपदैक्यता)
- Triple Verification: BPHS 4.8 (विना प्राणपदाच्छुद्धो...)
- Trine Rule (MANDATORY): BPHS 4.10 (प्राणपदं को राशि से त्रिकोण...)
- Special Lagnas: BPHS 4.18-28 (Bhava, Hora, Ghati, Varnada)
- Nisheka Lagna: BPHS 4.12-16 (Conception verification)

All candidates must pass the Trine Rule (BPHS 4.10) for human birth verification. Candidates are scored based on degree matching, Gulika/Moon alignment, and optional physical traits/life events verification.
